casebody.data:
Michael MARRANCA, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Valery LOYTSKER, Defendant. 078703
M-105/106 September Term 2017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 22, 2017

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-105) and file an overlength brief (M-106) are granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-107) is denied.
